<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root { --primary-color: #f9a825; --primary-light: #ffd54f; --primary-dark: #f57f17; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="text-center px-4">
    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-8xl mb-6" style="color: var(--primary-dark);"></i>
    <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">404</h1>
    <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8">Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</p>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Maaf, halaman yang Anda cari tidak tersedia.</p>
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-white font-semibold transition" style="background-color: var(--primary-dark);">
      <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i>
      Kembali ke Dashboard
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
